profile:
About
Your local experts in Roofing & Siding. Serving Huntsville, Muskoka & Surrounding areas for over 10 years.

Additional Information
Locally owned and operated for over 17 years, Milestone Roofing & Siding is a professional residential and commercial roofing & siding contractor. Milestone Roofing & Siding’s crews are professional artisans of their trade who deliver quality craftsmanship and provide outstanding customer experience.

When Milestone Roofing & Siding delivers your exterior solutions—you receive knowledgeable, experienced professionals who provide the exceptional level of quality for your home or business that we would want to receive in ours. Your complete satisfaction is our top priority.
Milestone Roofing & Siding welcomes the opportunity to put our extensive knowledge and expertise to work for you. Let us go the EXTRA MILE to help create your dream home!!

We're social here:
